get archives link "MAY 2013" WordPress Codex "Function Reference"
=================================================================

NAME
----

get archives link - Retrieve archive link content based on predefined or custom code.

SYNOPSIS
--------

Retrieve archive link content based on predefined or custom code.

The format can be one of four styles. The 'link' for head element,
'option' for use in the select element, 'html' for use in list (either
ol or ul HTML elements). Custom content is also supported using the
before and after parameters.

The 'link' format uses the link HTML element with the *archives*
relationship. The before and after parameters are not used. The text
parameter is used to describe the link.

The 'option' format uses the option HTML element for use in select
element. The value is the url parameter and the before and after
parameters are used between the text description.

The 'html' format, which is the default, uses the li HTML element for
use in the list HTML elements. The before parameter is before the link
and the after parameter is after the closing link.

The custom format uses the before parameter before the link ('a' HTML
element) and the after parameter after the closing link tag. If the
above three values for the format are not used, then custom format is
assumed.

USAGE
-----

` <?php get_archives_link( $url, $text, $format, $before, $after ); ?> `

PARAMETERS
----------

 `$url` 
:   ([*string*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*required*) URL to archive.
    Default: *None*

 `$text` 
:   ([*string*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*required*) Archive text description.
    Default: *None*

 `$format` 
:   ([*string*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) Optional, default is 'html'. Can be 'link', 'option',
    'html', or custom.
    Default: html

 `$before` 
:   ([*string*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) Optional.
    Default: empty string

 `$after` 
:   ([*string*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) Optional.
    Default: empty string

RETURN VALUES
-------------

 `` `(string)`{style="color:gray"} 
:   HTML link content for archive.

CHANGE LOG
----------

Since: [1.0](/Version_1.0 "Version 1.0")

SOURCE FILE
-----------

`get_archives_link()` is located in `wp-includes/general-template.php`

